title: ACTREC Recruitment 2026 - Walk-in-Interview for Lab Assistant Posts
description: The Advanced Centre for Treatment Research and Education in Cancer (ACTREC) has published the official notification for 2026. To fill up the various vacancies for Lab Assistant Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the 10th Pass can grab this chance and apply for the ACTREC Recruitment 2026 . Here, we included the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts.
